enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
section_title: MATTERS RELATING TO LEAST DEVELOPED COUNTRIES:
sentences: This item was introduced in the SBI 26 plenary on Monday, 7 May (FCCC/SBI/2007/12).
The Secretariat reported on this item and delegates agreed to appoint David Lesolle (Botswana) to conduct informal consultations, which resulted in the adoption of conclusions on 18 May.
